Regath is the owner of Regath's Wares in Arceuus.

Despite his shop being marked as a general store on the World map, his wares are more suitable for a magic shop. He plays a small role in the Client of Kourend quest.

Treasure Trails[edit | edit source]

Regath is the solution to the elite anagram clue: AT HERG. The answer to his elite challenge clue is 25.
